you met 12 years ago.

832
00:58:09,250 --> 00:58:12,280
If it’s necessary, we will finally meet, right?

833
00:58:12,280 --> 00:58:16,390
Open sesame!

834
00:58:18,310 --> 00:58:20,030
Professor Do!

835
00:58:20,030 --> 00:58:23,360
What an impolite guy!

836
00:58:23,360 --> 00:58:26,170
Being young and talented makes you supercilious?

837
00:58:26,170 --> 00:58:28,590
It’s useless to be talented.

838
00:58:28,590 --> 00:58:31,130
It’s cold-blooded!

839
00:58:31,130 --> 00:58:33,390
He probably hasn’t served in the army.

840
00:58:33,390 --> 00:58:36,270
The army is the best choice for that cruel guy.

841
00:58:36,270 --> 00:58:40,170
He is the one who should have a rough time.

842
00:58:40,170 --> 00:58:41,990
After being taught a lesson, he would be a man.

843
00:58:41,990 --> 00:58:43,960
-A real man!
-Yes, right.

844
00:58:45,260 --> 00:58:46,560
Be a soldier?

845
00:58:46,560 --> 00:58:49,470
Have you ever seen a soldier
in the war of America and Korea in 1871?

846
00:58:49,470 --> 00:58:52,920
No bulletproof vest, but cotton-padded coats.

847
00:58:52,920 --> 00:58:56,140
The 29 layered coats for bullet proofing.

848
00:58:56,140 --> 00:58:59,860
After liberation, I thought life would be easy.

849
00:58:59,860 --> 00:59:04,170
But the war separated the country into two.

850
00:59:04,170 --> 00:59:07,180
Later, I joined all air, sea and land forces.

851
00:59:07,180 --> 00:59:09,480
Because I have to update my ID every ten years.

852
00:59:09,480 --> 00:59:12,440
And thus I need to serve in the army again.

853
00:59:12,440 --> 00:59:16,690
People talk about PSY since he served twice.

854
00:59:16,690 --> 00:59:21,000
But I’ve served 24 times from Joseon Dynasty.

855
00:59:21,000 --> 00:59:23,110
It means I stayed in the army for 49 years

856
00:59:23,110 --> 00:59:25,990
and 7 months during the 400 years.

857
00:59:25,990 --> 00:59:27,880
Can you believe it?

858
00:59:28,930 --> 00:59:29,900
He should be sent to the Marine Corps!

859
00:59:29,900 --> 00:59:33,050
Marine Corps!
